race.comment: METHODS (8) finished out of the money two starts back then was beaten 7 lengths when fourth over 1207m at this track six weeks ago. Nicely placed to feature in the finish. ROCKITRETTA (6) went forward and gave a great sight before finishing second last time out over 1106m at this track (Dirt). Nicely placed to play a pivotal role. VERY UNLIKELY (4) did little and finished 11 lengths from the winner in seventh over 1408m at this track last start, a less impressive effort than her fifth at this track the run before. Finds the right race this time and can take this out. HAKUHIA (3) ran below expectations last start, finishing fifth and beaten 8 lengths at this track (Dirt) over 1673m. Should be competitive in this suitable race.
